{"tid":212820,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺要睇清另一半份人 最好既方法係由做純朋友開始","createTime":"2017-04-22T17:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T11:50:07.000Z","uid":58333,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea19b0c35f8009c785b60167f25739fd90ed3e1","tid":212820,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:22:13.000Z","msg":"例如一開始識左一個人<br />\n大家都有另一半 或者對大家都無興趣<br />\n大家都唔會特別點樣去討好另一方<br />\n唔會扮晒野<br />\n咁就可以將果個人份人睇得好清楚<br />\n到將來真係成為情侶果陣<br />\n因了解而分開既機會就少d啦<br />\n<br />\n例如可以睇得出 就算佢唔係想溝你<br />\n但仍然都會對你好有禮貌 唔會粗聲粗氣咁<br />\n就反映個人係有修養既<br />\n<br />\n又或者你有困難 佢都會諗盡辦法幫你<br />\n就可以反映到佢見義勇為"},{"pid":"1b4c486b5c4415426734bf8f849e12fba1d7b5ce","tid":212820,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:26:38.000Z","msg":"覺<br />\n不過女人唔會鐘意哩D男人"},{"pid":"24079bea1caa3f9ac5d54bd4119b38c86b1c8b25","tid":212820,"uid":55637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:27:27.000Z","msg":"熟落左咪又係一堆粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f0d56efc34c7455de4676af0158e0c8bc3be09","tid":212820,"uid":2659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:29:43.000Z","msg":"被人Friendzone咗再鐘意人好慘架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150146fb093227d3261b392c33be687eb7059088","tid":212820,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8f5a1da1168c48305f938c115741aafb9a9cf8","tid":212820,"uid":13260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"咁既情況9成都friendzone左"},{"pid":"38c4ed7c8233be83fdbee49a600bd9733529d632","tid":212820,"uid":69791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T18:17:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b9d77916e4bed0fd78